PN,40801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA 12-year-old girl died after she was
OL,8,Fhit by a falling branch while playing
OL,9,Fon a rope swing which "should have
OL,10,Fbeen removed" from a tree six months
OL,11,Fearlier, an inquest heard.
OL,13,FBrooke Wiggins died days before her
OL,14,F13th birthday on November 9 2024 in
OL,15,FBanstead, Surrey, after the impact of
OL,16,Fthe branch caused a fatal injury,
OL,17,FSouth London Coroner's Court heard on
OL,18,FWednesday.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe inquest heard the tree Brooke had
OL,8,Fbeen swinging from, maintained by
OL,9,FSurrey County Council, had been
OL,10,Finspected in May 2022 and was due for
OL,11,Fre-inspection in May 2024, which did
OL,12,Fnot take place.
OL,14,FActing on behalf of Brooke's father
OL,15,FLee Wiggins, Christian Weaver said
OL,16,Fthat had the inspection been carried
OL,17,Fout, any rope swing found on the tree
OL,18,Fshould have been removed, "as per
OL,19,Fpolicy".
OL,26,@zD@[OU{D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FRepresentatives for Surrey County
OL,8,FCouncil said expert evidence shows an
OL,9,Finspection may not have achieved a
OL,10,F"material different outcome".
OL,12,FIn statement read by assistant coroner
OL,13,FIvor Collett on behalf of Brooke's
OL,14,Fmother, Claire Etherington, she was
OL,15,Fdescribed as a "beautiful, fun, caring
OL,16,Fand loving girl" who had "the most
OL,17,Fincredible way of lighting up every
OL,18,Froom she went into".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@\O]wD@POUxD@PO]xD@ZOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"She was always surrounded by the
OL,8,Fpeople who loved her, and it's easy to
OL,9,Fsee why ` she gave so much love back,"
OL,10,Fher mother said.
OL,12,FBrooke loved dancing, art, singing and
OL,13,Ftaking photographs.
OL,15,FShe took pride in expressing herself,
OL,16,Fand "never went anywhere without her
OL,17,Feyelashes on", she said.
OL,19,F"She was a smart girl with so much
OL,20,Fpotential.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@fO]xD@EOUyD@MO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"We will always wonder what she would
OL,8,Fhave gone on to achieve in her life,"
OL,9,FMs Etherington said.
OL,11,FShe added that she hopes knowing what
OL,12,Fhappened to Brooke will bring "a small
OL,13,Fsense of closure" and "some
OL,14,Funderstanding".
OL,16,FIn a second statement read by Mr
OL,17,FCollett, Brooke's father told the
OL,18,Finquest his daughter was an "amazing
OL,19,Fyoung woman", who was "bright" and
OL,20,F"very funny".
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@eO]tD@_OUuD@QO]uD@WOUvD@NO]zD@
OL,26,A]OU{D@LO]{D@WOU{D@^O]|D@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe said: "I am devasted that my baby
OL,8,Fgirl has been taken from me.
OL,10,F"She packed so much into her short
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,F"Only 12 years old, and now she's gone
OL,14,Fforever.
OL,16,F"When I think of her, I ask myself,
OL,17,F'why my darling Brooke?'"
OL,26,@oD@JOUrD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"If only people had done their job
OL,8,Fproperly... the one thing they are
OL,9,Fpaid to do, and did it properly,
OL,10,FBrooke would still be here," Mr
OL,11,FWiggins added.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the start of the hearing,
OL,14,FMr Collett said: "This is a
OL,15,Fparticularly sad inquest.
OL,17,F"Of course, there are no happy
OL,18,Finquests, but this is dreadful because
OL,19,Fit concerns the death of a young child
OL,20,Fand there's no escaping that.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@\O]vD@ROUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776963955
OL,3,CGirl, 12, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cfalling branch on rope swing, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"To the family, I am bound to sound,
OL,8,Fat times, rather cold and distant...
OL,9,F(but) I do not take away for a moment
OL,10,Fthe unending pain felt by the family
OL,11,Fby the loss of their beloved daughter."
OL,13,FThe inquest continues.
